I also think VI intended this to be a raiding tool not something you do on an every day basis unless you raid everyday.  Just a thought.  BTW I do agree with the components being a bit much for the non uber guilds.  Some guilds don't have a few extra kp hanging around just to use for a quick evac that you might not use.<br>
<br>
